Text:
Downloaded this, it has no flaws, quality is what it says, no viruses; it's great!

Only one downfall--slow download, maybe more seeders would fix the problem. I just left it to download when I went to bed so no problems there!
I had this in 1980 and want to hear it again - can still remember a couple of the tracks in my head, so it sunk in pretty well. Thanks.
